  Description: "The Sudaram is the shroud of the dead. Once gaunt from hunger, it
    is now nourished by the power of the Nachzehrer King. For the Nachzehrer, consumption
    and nourishment\u2014greed and devotion\u2014are just two sides of the same dreaded
    coin."
  Skillset: "\u2022 Takes reduced damage from <color=#CC4000>Originium Pollutions</color>.\n\u2022
    While standing on an <color=#CC4000>Originium Pollution</color>, stops moving
    to gain increased ASPD. Attack range becomes global, and attacks now fire several
    projectiles."
